---
title: Cheesy BBQ Beef Loaded Wedges with Avocado Salsa & Sour Cream
description: Prepare for a table full of happy faces when you bring out this crowd-pleasing dish. With potato wedges, gently spiced beef mince, melted cheese, diced avocado salsa and sour cream, it's going all the way to number one!
